result.name: Cesto Cafe 藍地咖啡店

reviews.text: The price is reasonable .And put a cup of coffee on the desk, I will savor the taste of bitter, in fact, it is not enough for themselves but have bitter flavor.

Great quiet little cafe, if you need your caffeine fix and Starbucks just seems boring, this place has great coffee and makes delicious cappuccinos, the price is 20-35HKD making it extremely affordable and the beans are delicious. My only complaint is they lack an amenities stand, eg sugar, cream, milk, of course you can request it no problem but it's nice to have that in a coffee shop... the treats also look delicious, I haven't tried any yet but they have lots that you could imagine seeing at  any coffee shop, muffins, brownies, croisants, etc
